# Listing & Claim Gate

Product: marketplace listing title/description → Deci.Scoring → PASS/REVIEW/REJECT.
Stack: MF-style Go backend + Next SPA + Docker Compose (Postgres/API). Inference target: MLC container later.

## Non-negotiables

- Do not clone reference-project UI (DeciMind / TicketLens / mf-academy skins).
- Follow `.cursor/rules/frontend-design.mdc` visual system.
- Prompts, model id, and API secrets belong in DB (`system_prompts`, `app_settings`, `app_secrets`) — not hardcoded long-term.
- Mock + Manual Gate before real marketplace keys.
- ≥20 Go endpoints; auth stays on Go (Supabase = optional Postgres host only).

## Ops truth

- MCP (Render/Vercel/Academy) used at **deploy** time, not required for local Gate coding.
- Local: `docker compose up --build` for API+DB; frontend `npm run dev`.
